name: Standard Flier
description:
A standard HQ color flyer custom made and personalized to your event. I create fliers for parties, shows, concerts, and pretty much any other public event.

The order includes one high quality, singular layer, PNG image. If you scale the print, it should fit a standard piece of U.S. paper.

Once ordered, send an email to isaiahisherre@tmail.com with the following information:

NAME OF EVENT
TYPE OF EVENT (CONCERT, PARTY, ETC.)
VENUE NAME
ADDRESS
DATE, TIME
AGE RESTRICTION?/PRICE?
TICKETS IN ADVANCE/AT THE DOOR
PERFORMERS?

along with any other information.

name: Text Logo
description:
A high quality logo (with slogan) created in photoshop.

You'll receive one company logo (PNG in HQ).

Once ordered, please let me know any specifications you have for your logo.

Obviously, include your company name and slogan and ideal colors.

Send the information to isaiahisherre@tmail.com
